with the vice president, and campaigning and articulating a very
positive agenda of the future, of family and preserving our
freedoms, and preserving our hope and opportunity.
   Now obviously I intend to point out what would happen if the
party of McGovern, Carter, Mondale and Dukakis would somehow get
back in power.
   I think it would be a disaster.
